eolDate: Offical Cats project is no longer maintained.
description:
Blender 2.79 is significantly outdated and should generally be avoided. The official Cats project no longer supports this version.

If you have a specific reason to use this version, we've provided a link to the last known working build compatible with Blender 2.79.

Neither the official nor unofficial teams support this version, and we strongly recommend upgrading to a newer version of Blender. There is no wiki or support available, even on the Official Cats Discord.
